item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
Try our new Pimento Cheese it is delicious.

Mrs. Marshall’s fresh, delicious homemade salads—including her famous potato salad—have been a Richmond tradition since 1921. Since she introduced them at local grocers and delicatessens, they’ve become known for consistent quality and great taste.

[gallery columns="5" size="medium" ids="117,118,119,120,121"]

In 2005, the Ukrop family partnered with Mrs. Marshall’s and began producing the famous Potato Salad and Cole Slaw with the same love and attention to detail that the original family recipes required. Complementary items were also developed to provide new tastes for the many Mrs. Marshall’s fans. Today, Ukrop’s Homestyle Foods is honored to continue serving great-tasting Mrs. Marshall’s Potato Salad, Cole Slaw, Chicken Salad, BBQ, Pimento Cheese, Tuna Salad and Garden Pasta Salad.

Make Mrs. Marshall’s part of your next family dinner, cookout or picnic and discover Richmond’s tastiest tradition.

item.title: Mrs. Marshall's Potato Salad
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Starting with the finest russet potatoes and made-from-scratch mayonnaise, Richmond’s favorite potato salad comes garnished with a dollop of mayo and chives giving you a ready-to-serve delight for family and friends.

item.title: Mrs. Marshall's Chicken Salad
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: There’s nothing like made-from-scratch chicken salad—tender roasted chicken seasoned with a delicious blend of creamy mayonnaise and seasonings. It’s perfect as a side dish, on a bed of fresh lettuce or served on a White House Roll<sup>®</sup>.

item.title: Mrs. Marshall’s Cole Slaw
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Using a family recipe, our cole slaw is made with fresh shredded cabbage and carrots tossed in a light, tangy dressing. Enjoy it as a side or as the perfect complement to Mrs. Marshall’s BBQ.

item.title: Mrs. Marshall’s Seasoned Pulled Pork
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Our slow-cooked pulled pork comes in a sweet and tangy sauce giving you a rich, smoky flavor with just the right kick. Try Mrs. Marshall’s BBQ on a White House Roll<sup>®</sup> for a quick and delicious slider.

item.title: Mrs. Marshall’s Garden Pasta Salad
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: We’ve mixed fresh vegetables, perfectly cooked al dente macaroni, and a fresh tangy dressing with just the right touch of seasoning to create this refreshing, nourishing dish. Serve it with your favorite family-style meal. It’s sure to be a hit!

item.title: Mrs. Marshall’s Pimento Cheese
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Sharp cheddar cheese, mayonnaise and sweet pimento peppers together in one delicious spread. On a sandwich, as a dip with crackers or veggies, this is true southern comfort food.

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
